530
00:31:25.217 --> 00:31:27.276
No.

531
00:31:27.511 --> 00:31:28.736
No. te tenía que gustar.

532
00:31:28.970 --> 00:31:30.446
Nikki...

533
00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:32.490
Es un memorial.
Yo...

534
00:31:35.101 --> 00:31:36.953
No. es raro.

535
00:31:38.146 --> 00:31:40.706
No sé si es raro.
Bear.

536
